	<h1 class="title">「万物简史」汇丰：一个老牌帝国主义银行的中国发家史</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4696/small/4696.jpg?1418030328" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">苏琦 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-02 08:45:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/12918/medium/12918.jpg?1438463494" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


